'''長體多鋸鱸'''，為[[輻鰭魚綱|輻鰭魚綱]][[鱸形目|鱸形目]][[鱸亞目|鱸亞目]][[多鋸鱸科|多鋸鱸科]]的其中一[[種|種]]，分布於[[南半球|南半球]][[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]、[[智利|智利]][[巴塔哥尼亞|巴塔哥尼亞]]、[[澳洲|澳洲]]海域，為溫帶海水魚，深度50-854公尺，體長可達160公分，棲息在深海的底層水域，屬肉食性，以[[魚類|魚類]]等為食，可做為食用魚，適合各種烹飪方式食用，常作为高级食材，价格昂贵。<ref>National Institute of Water and Atmospheric Research, [https://www.niwa.co.nz/news-and-publications/publications/all/wa/vol.-18-no.1-july-2010/farmed-hapuku "Farmed hapuku a sizzling success with top seafood connoisseurs"] {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20121220085505/https://www.niwa.co.nz/news-and-publications/publications/all/wa/vol.-18-no.1-july-2010/farmed-hapuku |date=2012-12-20 }}, ''National Institute of Water and Atmospheric Research'', 2010. Retrieved September 12, 2010.</ref><ref name="OceanHunter">Ocean Hunter Ltd, [http://www.oceanhunter.co.nz/EDUCATION/Species+Identification/Hapuku.html "Hapuku"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.oceanhunter.co.nz/EDUCATION/Species+Identification/Hapuku.html |date=20100820213508 }}, ''OceanHunter'', n.d. Retrieved September 12, 2010.</ref>

